-- Jacuzzi shareholders approve takeover by Apollo Management
-- 
-- Thu Jan 25, 2007 4:47pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/01/25/us-jacuzzi-takeover-idUSWNAS850620070125

 

 (Reuters) - Jacuzzi Brands Inc. JJZ.N said its stockholders approved its merger with private equity firm Apollo Management L.P. 

 The deal is expected to close in early to mid-February 2007, the maker of whirlpool baths said in a statement. (Reporting by Amitha Rajan in Bangalore)